多倫多大學'''大会堂'''（{{Lang-en|Convocation Hall}}）位于加拿大[[安大略省|安大略省]][[多伦多|多伦多]]，是[[多伦多大学|多伦多大学]]的重要地标。这是一座圆顶的[[巨筒|圆形建筑]]。它是由Darling and Pearson设计，于1907年完工，其内部可与巴黎[[索邦大学|索邦大学]]的圆形剧场和牛津的[[谢尔登剧院|谢尔登剧院]]相比。<ref>{{Cite journal |url=http://www.magazine.utoronto.ca/great-gifts/alumni-launch-campaign-to-restore-convocation-hall/ |title=Alumni Launch Campaign to Restore Convocation Hall |journal=University of Toronto Magazine |year=2006 |issue=Spring 2006 |author=Raymer, Elizabeth |accessdate=2009-07-18 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728163538/https://magazine.utoronto.ca/campus/convocation-hall-restoration-alumni-campaign/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 虽然该建筑的名称表明它用于年度毕业典礼，但是它也是全年有大量听众参加的学术和社交活动的场所。<ref>{{Cite journal |url=http://www.magazine.utoronto.ca/feature/as-canadian-as-a-snowflake/ |title=As Canadian as a Snowflake |journal=University of Toronto Magazine |year=2002 |issue=Spring 2002 |author=Duffy, Dennis |accessdate=2009-07-18 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728163538/https://magazine.utoronto.ca/campus/places/famous-u-of-t-buildings-frank-darling-convocation-hall/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

大会堂包括四个楼层，可容纳1,731人。

